{
  "page": "Feature quote/179",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“There are those who say Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras</a> is a better jouster than <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(Longthorn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (Longthorn)\">Leo Longthorn</a> ever was.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a><br />“<a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly</a>'s little rose? I doubt that.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Tyrion V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406030341\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 85/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 303/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.583      1 -total\n100.00%    4.583      1 Template:Ref\n 63.01%    2.888      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key west